      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>Two fragments, not joining, from a <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">balustrade</rs>/parapet rim (of the same
kind as <xref type="inscription" n="92" href="010012">1.12</xref>-<xref type="inscription" n="96" href="010016">1.16</xref>) with
a smooth top, moulded front, rough back and lower edge (H. <measure dim="none">0.145</measure>, D.
<measure dim="none">0.175</measure>; W.: a: <measure dim="none">0.22</measure>; b: <measure dim="none">0.20</measure>).</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on upper rim.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p><measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.012-0.025</measure>;
clearly but very irregularly cut; diaeretic dots on <foreign lang="grc">Ι</foreign>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0700" exact="none" cert="low" notBefore="0401">Fifth to seventh centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
      </div>

      <div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
        <head lang="en">Edition</head>
			<div type="textpart_fragment" n="a"><ab>
				<lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved">ου</orig> <w lemma="σπουδή">σπουδῇ</w> <persName key="Ioannes5" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Ἰωάννης">Ἰωάννου</name></persName> 
				</ab></div><div type="textpart_fragment" n="b"><ab><lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved">ως</orig> <w lemma="οὗτος">τού<unclear reason="damage">τ</unclear>ου</w> <orig n="unresolved">α<unclear reason="damage">ι</unclear></orig><gap dim="right" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
			</ab></div> 
      </div>

      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <p>a.  <gap dim="left" reason="lost"/> by the effort of
<seg cert="low">John</seg> <gap dim="right" reason="lost"/></p>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head><p>For discussion see <xref type="eAla-text" n="VII.22">VII.22</xref>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="history" n="locations"><head>Locations</head><p>Found: <rs type="found">a. <rs type="monuList" key="Temple">Temple/Church</rs>: East Temenos area—surface find during clearing; b.
<rs type="monuList" key="Acropolis">Acropolis</rs> in 1970</rs>. Original location: <rs type="origLocation">An unidentified church: crowning the chancel barrier</rs>. Last recorded location: <rs type="lastLocation">Museum (1978)</rs>. </p></div>

      

      

